## NativeWind
- Use className prop for styling (className="bg-blue-500 p-4") instead of StyleSheet
- Use dark: prefix for dark mode (className="bg-white dark:bg-black")
- Extend tailwind.config.js for custom colors, spacing, or components

## Best Practices
- Maintain consistent spacing with p-[number] and m-[number] classes
- Create responsive layouts with flex, justify, and items classes
- Group related styles into reusable className strings
- Use dynamic classes with template literals for conditional styling
- Add tw-prefixed comments for complex className strings
- Avoid inline styles when NativeWind classes would work

## Typography & Colors
- Use consistent typography with text-* classes for size and weight
- Use color palette from tailwind.config.js theme

## Images
- Use appropriate resizeMode and dimensions for images
- Implement proper aspect ratios with NativeWind classes

## Spacing
- Prefer flex with gap over space-x/space-y
